Rick Overton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rick_Overton 0 Richard Overton (born August 10, 1954) is an American screenwriter, actor and comedian. His writing credits include Dennis Miller Live, and his acting credits include Willow and The Secret Adventures of Jules Verne.
